1.8.0 (2020-03-25)
------------------

* Feature - Amazon CloudWatch Application Insights for .NET and SQL Server now integrates with Amazon CloudWatch Events (AWS CodeDeploy, AWS Health and Amazon EC2 state changes). This feature enables customers to view events related to problems detected by CloudWatch Application Insights, and reduce mean-time-to-resolution (MTTR).

1.6.0 (2020-01-20)
------------------

* Feature - This release adds support for a list API to retrieve the configuration events logged during periodic updates to an application by Amazon CloudWatch Application Insights.

1.5.0 (2019-11-25)
------------------

* Feature - CloudWatch Application Insights for .NET and SQL Server includes the follwing features: -Tagging Create and manage tags for your applications.-Custom log pattern matching. Define custom log patterns to be detected and monitored.-Resource-level permissions. Specify applications users can access.
